Wil Horneff https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wil_Horneff 0 William Samuel "Wil" Horneff (born June 12, 1979) is an American former child actor who won two Young Artist Awards from three nominations. Horneff opened "Training Grounds Jiu-Jitsu MMA", where he teaches Brazilian jiu-jitsu, after leaving his career.
